Adam Robitel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adam_Robitel 0 Adam Robitel (born May 28, 1978) is an American film director, producer, screenwriter, and actor. He directed and co-wrote the 2014 film The Taking of Deborah Logan, was the co-writer for the 2015 film Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension, and directed the 2018 film Insidious: The Last Key.
